      "body" : "It would be better to store a value like \"lastCompleteSyncCount\", which keeps track of the last block at which the client was 100% synced with the network. Clients that quit in the middle of a block download will keep their progress, which will reduce frustration. Additionally, clients that are synced when they were shut down will see their actual progress, instead of seeing 99% every time.",
